Name: Parkinson's disease
Definition: A synucleinopathy that has_material_basis_in degeneration of the central nervous system that often impairs motor skills

Name: multiple system atrophy
Definition: A placenta disease that is characterized by an abnormally deep attachment of the placenta

Name: obsolete Dictyocaulus infectious disease
Definition: A trichostrongyloidiasis that involves parasitic infection of the bronchial tree of horses
